title: Would have given it '0'
review: One of the worst films I have ever seen.This film and my vote are the sole reason for my registration on IMDb! It is that bad! I noticed it was sitting in the top 200 films of all time and decided something must be done to change this.In all seriousness, do not bother watching this film. So much of the acting is cringe-worthy and the dialogue is continuously poor. Look out for Angelina's 'love-interest'.Over and out.Eltommo
